      "role": "user",
      "content": "I see. It sounds like you're saying the benefits are pretty much guaranteed if certain safeguards are in place. But isn't it true that for many people, like tradespeople or delivery drivers, there really isn't a \"sustainable\" alternative to driving, so these exemptions often don't actually solve the immediate financial hit they take?",
